<h1>New monoGame Ideas</h1>
<p>

<ol>
<li>We are going to introduce in Beta a new Faction Reward NFT that is governed by the game play <em>daily rewards</em>.
It will be up to players to play which will reflect the abilities of the future Reward NFT. This will rely on players
ability to complete daily rewards, the more players complete daily rewards the more skill levels that faction Reward NFT
will have. Each member of that faction will receive the future Reward Card for free.</li>
</ol>

</p>
